lead_paragraph: Makayla Epps and Evelyn Akhator scored 13 points apiece and No. 19 Kentucky ended Radford's seven-game winning streak 59-36 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Epps, Akhator Have 13, No. 19 Kentucky Women Stifle Radford
